outputs.output_descr: This new phase of the project aims to provide advisory services to the Government to update and implement the National Spatial Strategy (NSS) which was produced under a previous phase of the project. The project will specifically develop the national capacities in terms of institutional and individual competencies within the Ministry to sustain the achievements of urban planning that were materialized in the last two decades.

project_descr: Updating the National Spatial Strategy and promoting the national Urban observatory network

subnational.name: Ministry of Economy and Planning, Riyadh
